text: Marie Anne de Bourbon, Légitimée de France (2 October 1666 - 3 May 1739) was the eldest legitimised daughter (fille légitimée de France) of King Louis XIV of France and his first well known mistress Louise de La Vallière.RUE NEUVE- SAINT-AUGUSTINS. „Marie-Anne, fille légitimée de Louis XIV et de Mme de Lavallière” == References == Category:1666 births Category:1739 deaths Marie Anne Marie Anne Category:Smallpox survivors Category:People from Val-de-Marne
